                        <interp inst="t18440506-name-156" type="given" value="WARD STAN"></interp>WARD STAN WELL</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a constable of Islington. I saw the prisoner run<lb></lb>ning in a direction from Harris's shop—Harris collared him—he immediately turned round and struck him a violent blow on the head—I secured him.</p>
